        <mxCell id="71" parent="70" value="&lt;b&gt;SPECIFICATIONS SUMMARY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Operating System:&lt;/b&gt; Windows Server x64 2025 (all servers)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Database:&lt;/b&gt; Microsoft SQL Server 2022 (2 instances: Non-Prod + Prod)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;WebLogic Version:&lt;/b&gt; 14.1.2.0.0 (JAS &amp; AIS servers, 3 instances each: 1 non-prod, 2 prod)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;JDK:&lt;/b&gt; 17.0.14 or 1.8.0_491&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Key Ports:&lt;/b&gt; RDP (3389), JDE Enterprise (5150), WebLogic JAS (8998-8999), SQL Server (1433 default or custom TBD)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Security:&lt;/b&gt; SSL/TLS certificates required, Password policies enforced (No $ or ! in WebLogic, restricted chars in SQL Server)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Infrastructure Support:&lt;/b&gt; One-Click Provisioning, Deployment Server (Oracle 19.0), Apache Load Balancer&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Total Servers: 11 types (~17 instances) | CPU: 41 cores | RAM: 168 GB | Storage: ~1,290 GB&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;align=left;fontSize=8;whiteSpace=wrap" vertex="1">
